│ This assertion compares the vectorization factor (VF) chosen by the VPlan-native path cost model (`BestFactor.Width`) with   │
│ the one chosen by the legacy cost model (`LegacyVF.Width`). They are expected to be the same, unless the VPlan can perform   │
